         <p class="text-[16px] leading-8 mb-2"> Banks and financial institutions are obligated to follow regulatory guidelines, RBI circulars, and statutory recovery procedures. </p>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-8"> Borrowers and customers have the right to fair treatment, transparency, and lawful enforcement of contractual terms. </p>
